      "value": "<p><em><strong>Path of Witchcraft:</strong> 13th and 17th level</em></p>\n<p>You've learned to absorb the fleeting magicks of your familiar. When your familiar is destroyed by taking damage, you can choose to grant temporary hit points equal to [[/r 2d8]] + your Wisdom or Charisma modifier (your choice) to one friendly creature of your choice you can see within 30 feet.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature five times. You gain an additional use at 17th level. You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
